{
  "npc": "undeadwoman",
  "game": 1,
  "avatar": "/icons/ds1/dialogues/undeadwoman.webp",
  "lines": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "chn": "#0第1次攀谈",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:1回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-1st time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "chn": "啊，你人没事是吗？",
      "jap": "ああ、あんた、まともな人かい？",
      "eng": "Hmm, you still have your senses about you?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "chn": "那你要不要买一些我的苔藓？",
      "jap": "だったら、あたしの苔を買っておくれよ",
      "eng": "Then why won't you buy some of my moss?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "chn": "我想要你的灵魂啊。",
      "jap": "あんたのソウルが欲しいんだよ",
      "eng": "I need your souls!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "chn": "#0第2次攀谈",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:2回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-2nd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "chn": "啊！你又来了啊。",
      "jap": "ああ、あんた、またきてくれたのかい？",
      "eng": "Oh, there you are, dearie!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "chn": "我好开心喔。",
      "jap": "あたしゃ嬉しいよ",
      "eng": "A pleasure to see you again.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "chn": "#0第3次攀谈",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:3回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-3rd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "chn": "啊，你来啦。",
      "jap": "ああ、あんた、きてくれたのかい？",
      "eng": "Oh, there you are, dearie!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "chn": "苔藓我有，拿灵魂来换吧。",
      "jap": "苔ならあるよ。あんたのソウルをお出しよ",
      "eng": "I have moss; now dish up some souls!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "chn": "#0离开城外不死镇后，返回攀谈",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:4回目",
      "eng": "#0Talk-After leaving & returning to Undead Burg",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "chn": "啊，是你啊。",
      "jap": "ああ、あんたかい？",
      "eng": "Oh, hello, dearie.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "chn": "有一段时间没看到你啦，",
      "jap": "随分と久しぶりじゃないか",
      "eng": "You left me high and dry for a while, there.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "chn": "我好寂寞喔。",
      "jap": "あたしゃ寂しかったよ",
      "eng": "I thought maybe you'd forgotten about me.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "chn": "你想要我的苔藓对吧？",
      "jap": "あたしの苔が欲しいんだろう？",
      "eng": "Are you back for more of my moss, then?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "chn": "我为你收集的，全都要给你的喔。",
      "jap": "あんたのために集めておいたんだ。たーんとあげるよ",
      "eng": "Plenty of it here. Freshly peeled, just for you!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "chn": "#0互动列表-第1次选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すA",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 1st time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "chn": "你来得真不是时候。",
      "jap": "あんたも、大変なところにきちまったね",
      "eng": "You've come to this land at a bad time.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "chn": "这里几乎没有人是正常的，\r\n差不多剩下我啦。",
      "jap": "この地には、まともな人なんてほとんどいない。\r\nあたしくらいさ",
      "eng": "There are nothing but Hollows in these parts.\r\nSave for me, of course.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "chn": "你也是不死人吧？要小心啊。",
      "jap": "あんたも、不死なんだろう？せいぜい気をつけておくれよ",
      "eng": "You're Undead, too, aren't you? You be careful, then.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "chn": "#0互动列表-第2次选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すB",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 2nd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "chn": "嗯，从这里下去，\r\n就可以到不死镇的底层。",
      "jap": "ああ、この横を下りれば、\r\n不死街の最下層につながってるよ",
      "eng": "Ah, go down along the side\r\nto reach the depths of the Undead Burg.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "chn": "那里全都是些肮脏污秽又下贱的家伙，",
      "jap": "不潔で汚い、下賎の連中だけがいるところさ",
      "eng": "Only unkempt crooks and liars to be found there.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "chn": "总之那里与我无缘。",
      "jap": "まあ、あたしには無縁の場所だけどねえ",
      "eng": "Hardly a place for a lady like myself!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "chn": "你的话，我就不知道了。",
      "jap": "あんたは、どうなんだろうねえ？",
      "eng": "But who knows, maybe you'd fit right in?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "chn": "嘻嘻嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "chn": "#0互动列表-第3次选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "ここは、すばらしい場所だろう？",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 3rd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "chn": "这里很棒对吧？",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すC",
      "eng": "This is a wonderful place, don't you think?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "chn": "有水有苔藓又潮湿，\r\n还有铁栏杆，",
      "jap": "水もあって、苔もあって\r\nずっとジメジメして、鉄格子まである",
      "eng": "We have water, moss, moisture,\r\nthese nice iron bars...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "chn": "我非常喜欢这里。",
      "jap": "あたしゃ、この場所が好きなんだ",
      "eng": "I like it here, I really do.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "chn": "从以前到现在，都没遇到过一件好事，",
      "jap": "昔っから、いいことなんか１つもありゃしなかったんだから",
      "eng": "Nothing good ever happened to me in life.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "chn": "自从变成不死人，现在是最幸福的。",
      "jap": "不死になって、今が一番幸せさね",
      "eng": "But now that I'm Undead, I've never been happier!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "chn": "#0互动列表-第4次选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "ねえ、あんた…",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 4th time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "chn": "我在收集苔藓。",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すD",
      "eng": "I forage moss.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "chn": "这城镇越是往下，\r\n就越是充满了毒与疾病那种不干净的东西。",
      "jap": "あたしゃ、苔を集めてるんだ",
      "eng": "In the lower areas of this town,\r\nyou'll find all kinds of poison and pestilence.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "chn": "谁都一样，没有了苔藓就完蛋了。",
      "jap": "この街は、下にいけばいくほど\r\n毒だとか疫病だとか、不潔なものばかりだからね",
      "eng": "You can't travel a stone's toss without some trusty moss.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "chn": "你也是，所以要多带一点去喔。",
      "jap": "誰だって、苔がなくっちゃあ、どうしようもないのさ",
      "eng": "Make sure you take plenty with you!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "あんたも、たーんと持っていかなくちゃねえ？",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "chn": "#0互动列表-第5次选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 5th time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "chn": "我问你喔……",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すE",
      "eng": "Tell me honestly...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "chn": "你心里面一定觉得……",
      "jap": "あんた、本当は思ってるんじゃないかい？",
      "eng": "You think I've gone to the other side, don't you?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "chn": "我不正常了，对吧？",
      "jap": "あたしは、もう、まともじゃないって…",
      "eng": "That I've cracked my head and gone Hollow...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "chn": "你说实话啊，",
      "jap": "そうなんだろう、あんた？",
      "eng": "You do, don't you?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "chn": "不要不讲话，",
      "jap": "黙ってるんじゃないよ",
      "eng": "I can see it in your eyes.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "chn": "我知道你在想什么……",
      "jap": "あたしには分かるんだよ…",
      "eng": "You'd trust a patch of moss over me...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "chn": "#0第1次未完成交易，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(何もしかなった):A",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" 1st time without purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "chn": "不买啊……",
      "jap": "なんだい…",
      "eng": "Drat.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "chn": "#2（男主角）#3真是不给情面的男生耶……",
      "jap": "つまらない男だね…",
      "eng": "What a humdrum lad you are.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "chn": "#2（女主角）#3真是不给情面的女生耶……",
      "jap": "つまらない女だね…",
      "eng": "What a humdrum lass you are.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "chn": "#0第2次未完成交易，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(何もしなかった):B",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" 2nd time without purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "chn": "哼，好吧。",
      "jap": "フン、そうかい",
      "eng": "Hmph, fine, then.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "chn": "你可不要后悔。",
      "jap": "後悔すればいいのさ",
      "eng": "But you'll regret it.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "chn": "#0第3次未完成交易，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(何もしなかった):C",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" 3rd time without purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "chn": "怎么，你耍我啊？",
      "jap": "なんだい、からかってるのかい？",
      "eng": "Are you toying with me?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "chn": "你一定不会有好下场的。",
      "jap": "きっと碌なことにならないよ、あんた",
      "eng": "One day, your fate will catch up with you.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "chn": "因为我知道啊……",
      "jap": "あたしには分かるんだ…",
      "eng": "I have a sense for these things...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "chn": "举头三尺有神明……",
      "jap": "神様は、いつも見てるんだよ…",
      "eng": "The Gods above are watching you!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "chn": "#0第1次完成交易后，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(買い物などをした):A",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" 1st time after purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "chn": "请再来啊。",
      "jap": "またきておくれよ",
      "eng": "Come again, if you please!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "chn": "嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "chn": "#0第2次完成交易后，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(買い物などをした):B",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" 2nd time after purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "chn": "真是多谢啦。",
      "jap": "たーんと、どうもね",
      "eng": "Much obliged.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "chn": "我喜欢你喔。",
      "jap": "あたしゃ、あんた好きだよ",
      "eng": "I think I like you!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "chn": "嘻嘻嘻嘻",
      "jap": "フヒヒヒヒッ",
      "eng": "Vee hee hee hee hee!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "chn": "#0走开中断对话",
      "jap": "#0彼女から離れて",
      "eng": "#0After leaving abruptly",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "chn": "你要去哪啊！",
      "jap": "あんた、どこいくんだい！",
      "eng": "Don't run off!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "chn": "#0走开中断对话后，返回攀谈",
      "jap": "#0話しかけた:離れてから戻った",
      "eng": "#0Talk-After leaving abruptly",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "chn": "发生什么事啊你？",
      "jap": "どうしたってんだい、まったく",
      "eng": "What's the matter with you!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "chn": "连我都被吓一跳。",
      "jap": "あたしだって、びっくりするじゃないか",
      "eng": "Don't you toy with my nerves!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "chn": "#0第1次受到攻击时",
      "jap": "#0攻撃した:1回目",
      "eng": "#0Upon being attacked-1st time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "chn": "等一下！",
      "jap": "ちょっと！",
      "eng": "Why, you!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "chn": "#0第2次受到攻击时",
      "jap": "#0攻撃した:2回目",
      "eng": "#0Upon being attacked-2nd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "chn": "住手！",
      "jap": "やめとくれよ！",
      "eng": "Stop that!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "chn": "#0第3次受到攻击时",
      "jap": "#0攻撃した:3回目",
      "eng": "#0Upon being attacked-3rd time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "chn": "好痛！",
      "jap": "いたいっ！",
      "eng": "Ouch!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "chn": "#0第4次受到攻击时",
      "jap": "#0攻撃した:4回目",
      "eng": "#0Upon being attacked-4th time",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "chn": "啊！",
      "jap": "キャアッ！",
      "eng": "Eeek!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "chn": "#0攻击导致敌对时",
      "jap": "#0敵対状態になった",
      "eng": "#0Upon being attacked & made hostile",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "chn": "你做什么啊！",
      "jap": "あんた、なにすんのよ！",
      "eng": "What do you think you're doing?!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "chn": "我可也不是让人欺侮大的！",
      "jap": "あたしだって、一端のものさ！",
      "eng": "I have my pride, you damn fool!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
